---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Electronic Systems & IoT Services | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="IoT and embedded systems services - smart solutions for connected devices in the UAE."
  path="/services/electronic-systems/"
>

  <section class="service-content" id="iot-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2>Electronic Systems & IoT Services</h2>
      <p>We design, develop, and deploy comprehensive IoT and embedded systems solutions that bridge the physical and digital worlds. Our expertise spans hardware integration, firmware development, cloud connectivity, and intelligent analytics.</p>

      <h3>IoT Platform Development</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>End-to-End Solutions</h4><p>Complete IoT ecosystems from device management to cloud analytics, mobile apps, and dashboard interfaces.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Device Management</h4><p>Scalable platforms for provisioning, monitoring, and managing thousands of connected devices remotely.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Real-Time Analytics</h4><p>Process and analyze sensor data in real-time for actionable insights and automated responses.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Cloud Integration</h4><p>Seamless integration with AWS IoT, Azure IoT Hub, and Google Cloud IoT for scalable infrastructure.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Embedded Systems Development</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Microcontroller Programming:</strong> Firmware for ARM, AVR, PIC, ESP32, and STM32</li>
        <li><strong>RTOS Development:</strong> Real-time operating systems including FreeRTOS, Zephyr, and custom implementations</li>
        <li><strong>Embedded Linux:</strong> Custom Linux distributions, kernel modules, and device drivers</li>
        <li><strong>Low-Power Design:</strong> Power-optimized firmware for battery-operated devices</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Smart Home & Building Automation</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Home Automation</h4><p>Smart control systems for lighting, climate, security, and entertainment integrated with voice assistants.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Building Management</h4><p>Comprehensive BMS for commercial buildings including HVAC, lighting, access control, and energy monitoring.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Energy Management</h4><p>Smart metering, energy monitoring, and optimization systems to reduce consumption and costs.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Security Systems</h4><p>Advanced security solutions with cameras, sensors, facial recognition, and automated alerts.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Industrial IoT (IIoT)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Predictive Maintenance:</strong> Monitor equipment health and predict failures before they occur</li>
        <li><strong>Asset Tracking:</strong> Real-time location and condition monitoring of valuable assets</li>
        <li><strong>Process Automation:</strong> Automated control systems for manufacturing and production lines</li>
        <li><strong>Quality Control:</strong> Automated inspection and quality assurance using sensors and vision systems</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Wireless Communication Technologies</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>WiFi & Bluetooth</h4><p>Short-range wireless solutions including BLE, WiFi 6, and mesh networking protocols.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Cellular IoT</h4><p>4G/5G, NB-IoT, and LTE-M connectivity for wide-area IoT applications.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>LPWAN Technologies</h4><p>LoRaWAN, Sigfox, and low-power wide-area networks for long-range communications.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Zigbee & Z-Wave</h4><p>Home automation protocols for reliable, low-power mesh networks.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>IoT Security</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Device Authentication:</strong> Secure device identity and certificate-based authentication</li>
        <li><strong>Encrypted Communication:</strong> TLS/SSL encryption for data in transit</li>
        <li><strong>OTA Updates:</strong> Secure over-the-air firmware updates with rollback capability</li>
        <li><strong>Threat Detection:</strong> Anomaly detection and intrusion prevention systems</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Our Tech Stack</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Hardware Platforms:</strong> Arduino, Raspberry Pi, ESP32, STM32, Nordic nRF, Qualcomm</li>
        <li><strong>Firmware Languages:</strong> C, C++, Rust, MicroPython, Assembly</li>
        <li><strong>RTOS:</strong> FreeRTOS, Zephyr, Mbed OS, Azure RTOS</li>
        <li><strong>IoT Protocols:</strong> MQTT, CoAP, HTTP/HTTPS, WebSocket, AMQP</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud Platforms:</strong> AWS IoT, Azure IoT, Google Cloud IoT, ThingSpeak</li>
        <li><strong>Development Tools:</strong> PlatformIO, STM32CubeIDE, ESP-IDF, Keil, IAR</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container"><div class="contact-content">
      <h2>Let's Build Something Great Together</h2>
      <p>Ready to transform your business with cutting-edge technology solutions? Get in touch with our team today.</p>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br>Get in touch</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span></div>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </section>

</Layout>
